{"word":"G837 - αὐξάνω - auxánō - owx-an'-o - Grow","slug":"G837","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αὐξάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>auxánō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>owx-an'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Grow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03BE;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - auxano&#x0304;</b> - <i>owx-an'-o</i><p/>A prolonged form of a primary verb; to <i>grow</i> (&ldquo;wax&rdquo;), that is, <i>enlarge</i> (literally or figuratively, actively or passively): - grow (up), (give the) increase."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5232\">G5232</a>"}]}